3.555, 153.5545, 154.0221, 153.9238, 153.8249, 154.0448, 153.8975, 154.6482, 152.9658, 151.6628, 151.8758, 154.1325, 153.5595, 153.6925, 154.5573, 154.3748, 155.3197, 160.9241, 165.6393, 165.321, 165.3074, 164.2743, 165.8195, 166.8507, 168.9972, 168.7692, 167.1823, 166.2436, 166.8555, 166.2043, 165.2327, 163.8349, 163.6037, 164.2765, 165.059, 165.1894, 164.2082, 164.089, 164.7157, 165.1134, 165.7172, 166.8263, 167.2386, 166.8326, 167.3709, 167.0168, 166.4546, 167.4096, 166.4441, 167.3521, 166.0065, 168.1285, 168.3917, 167.5352, 167.2218, 168.721, 168.4451, 169.3946, 170.876, 172.8235, 172.1829, 171.412, 174.293, 176.3174, 176.3543, 176.5889, 177.4905, 176.3138, 177.4419, 174.911, 175.4546, 175.2872, 175.6062, 175.0859, 172.6569, 173.6635, 173.7509, 173.8314, 171.4726, 169.5898, 170.3079, 171.187, 170.8185, 167.9881, 166.9808, 166.1287, 165.2102, 167.3837, 167.6818, 164.5274, 163.4164, 163.791, 160.336, 162.8696, 162.4095, 161.9758, 161.5169, 165.5671, 168.2275, 166.6084, 165.4808, 167.817, 166.4672, 166.1695, 165.9883, 163.7106, 164.7606, 164.2411, 160.9873, 161.2468, 161.7136, 159.6614, 156.1717, 155.8993, 154.8245, 154.4319, 150.8066, 148.0738, 150.7887, 149.2443, 148.6633, 150.0548, 147.4161, 147.725, 145.3455, 145.8426, 147.2035, 148.0649, 147.7832, 149.6841, 146.7013, 145.9792, 148.0941, 147.2232, 150.2328, 144.0849, 143.5916, 141.6534, 149.9526, 144.7779, 147.4085, 146.7239, 148.2758, 149.5945, 150.3867, 153.9387, 153.8402, 152.9532, 153.6651, 152.4045, 151.9074, 150.9733, 149.0481, 148.7605, 149.4399, 152.0762, 154.3878], "summary_html": "<h1>因子择时：截面离散度条件动量/反转</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报提出用宏观经济、金融市场和因子表现三个层次的择时变量预测选股因子收益。核心发现：市场波动率和收益离散度与反转/动量因子的有效性存在稳定的跨期相关性。高波动/高离散度环境下反转因子有效（前期下跌的品种未来反弹），低波动/低离散度环境下动量因子有效（前期强势品种继续走强）。</p>\n<p>翻译到商品期货：计算截面收益离散度的 Z-score 作为 regime 指标，与截面动量因子相乘得到时变信号。离散度高时信号翻转为反转逻辑，离散度低时保持动量逻辑。该因子捕捉了市场状态对动量/反转效应切换的预测能力。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.74</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-10.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3285</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.96</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.18 / 0.78</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.91</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.03</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.39</span></td><td>0.99</td><td>1.84</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.07</span></td><td>1.32</td><td>0.32</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.05</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.4</span></td><td>1.38</td><td>0.1</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.6</span></td><td>1.69</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.57</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3287</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>40.4</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>截面离散度:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\sigma_{cs,t} = \\text{std}(r_{i,t})_{i=1}^{N}, \\quad \\bar{\\sigma}_{cs,t}^{(w)} = \\frac{1}{w}\\sum_{s=t-w+1}^{t} \\sigma_{cs,s}</div>\n<p>离散度 regime Z-score:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Z_{disp,t} = \\frac{\\bar{\\sigma}_{cs,t}^{(w)} - \\mu_{L}(\\bar{\\sigma}_{cs}^{(w)})}{\\sigma_{L}(\\bar{\\sigma}_{cs}^{(w)})}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_L</span>, <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_L</span> 是过去 <span class=\"math-tex\">L</span> 天的滚动均值和标准差。</p>\n<p>因子择时信号:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">S_{i,t} = -Z_{disp,t} \\times \\text{mom}_{i,t}^{(k)}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{mom}_{i,t}^{(k)} = P_{i,t}/P_{i,t-k} - 1</span> 是品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 的 <span class=\"math-tex\">k</span> 日动量。负号确保：高离散度（正 Z）翻转动量方向成为反转信号。</p>\n<p>仓位:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{pos}_{i,t} = \\text{rank}(S_{i,t}) \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1</strong> (Sharpe 0.55): 初始实现，尝试了波动率regime择时、离散度regime择时、波动率变化反转三类因子。离散度择时(21d momentum, 21d regime, 252d lookback)最优但换手率1.07过高。</p>\n<p><strong>R2</strong> (Sharpe 0.69): 扩展参数网格（momentum 5/10/21/63d, hold 5/10/21d），增加IC-gating。最优配置移到hold=10d，但turnover升至1.75。IC-gating无明显帮助。</p>\n<p><strong>R3</strong> (Sharpe 0.98): 关键突破——将momentum lookback延长至42d（更稳健的趋势信号），regime lookback缩短至126d（更快适应市场状态变化），增加regime信号的EMA平滑。最终最优: m42_r10_l126_h21，Sharpe从0.69跳升至0.98，turnover降至0.97。5个变体超过0.85。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（57个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 月度换仓（21天）</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>: 截面因子（截面离散度条件的动量/反转切换）</li>\n<li><strong>冗余检查</strong>: 与因子库最大相关性 0.19，为新信号</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 2017年和2024年Sharpe为负，策略在市场regime持续单边时可能失效；研报原始逻辑依赖宏观/债市数据（PPI、利率、TED利差等），此处仅使用了可从商品数据计算的截面离散度作为regime指标，是原文的部分复现</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.25s</li>\n</ul>"}